OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774631479
OL,3,CAlleged far-right extremist planned
OL,4,Cattack on asylum hotel in Hull, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAn alleged far-right extremist planned
OL,8,Fto attack an asylum hotel in Hull, a
OL,9,Fcourt had heard.
OL,11,FMikka Lee Anderson appeared at the Old
OL,12,FBailey on Friday charged with
OL,13,Fpreparing acts of terrorism between
OL,14,FMay 2025 ad February this year.
OL,16,FThe 23-year-old allegedly identified a
OL,17,Fhotel in Hull city centre that was
OL,18,Fhousing asylum seekers and tried to
OL,19,Frecruit a helper, who reported the
OL,20,Fdefendant to the police.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774631479
OL,3,CAlleged far-right extremist planned
OL,4,Cattack on asylum hotel in Hull, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe court heard Anderson allegedly
OL,8,Fplanned the attack in the wake of the
OL,9,FJuly 2024 Southport stabbings.
OL,11,FIt is also alleged he had a collection
OL,12,Fof knives and weapons, a lock knife, a
OL,13,Fcopy of The Anarchist Cookbook and a
OL,14,Fdocument on homemade firearms.
OL,16,FAnderson, from Hull, was arrested on
OL,17,F26 February by counter-terrorism
OL,18,Fpolice.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774631479
OL,3,CAlleged far-right extremist planned
OL,4,Cattack on asylum hotel in Hull, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FIn addition to the alleged attack
OL,8,Fplan, he was charged with possession
OL,9,Fof articles for a terrorist purpose,
OL,10,Ftwo counts of possessing information
OL,11,Fof a kind likely to be useful to a
OL,12,Fperson committing or preparing an act
OL,13,Fof terrorism and having an article
OL,14,Fwith a blade in a public place.
OL,16,FHe appeared at the Old Bailey on
OL,17,FFriday by videolink from custody for a
OL,18,Fpreliminary hearing.
OL,20,FAnderson has been remanded in custody.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
